  "texts": [
    "GPT-4 can produce code from docstrings in software engineering interviews and answer coding questions on par with or better than human performance.",
    "It is capable of interacting with LaTeX and front-end programming.",
    "It can run Python, Pseudo, and reverse engineer programs.",
    "The company that created GPT-4, OpenAI, provides programmatic access to its LLMs.",
    "These advanced LLMs, such as GPT-4, represent a paradigm shift in computing, harnessing vast knowledge and understanding of context to perform complex tasks."
